description: ![header](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69332964/114803220-14269100-9d6d-11eb-9a3a-e92a637e5d79.png) ## Intro To Serverless Pair-Programming *Throughout the bootcamp, you will be presented with a problem each week that aims to reinforce the skills you learned that week.* ### ✏️ Guidelines * You will work with a partner * Whoever is "driving" that week will submit their code on behalf of you both * Fork this repo to get started!
